Feature	        Kotlin mutableListOf()	          C++ std::list
Can grow/shrink 	✅ Yes	                          ✅ Yes
Allows element modification	✅ Yes                ✅ Yes
Backed by	Usually ArrayList (dynamic array)       	Doubly linked list
Performance (random access)	✅ Fast (O(1))	       ❌ Slow (O(n))
Performance (insertion/removal in middle)	         ❌ Slow (O(n))	✅ Fast (O(1) if you have iterator) 
